n in my restaurants.”<p><br><p><i>A version of this story first appeared in <a href="https://cardinalnews.org/2023/08/16/chef-sean-brock-brings-appalachia-to-the-masses/?utm_source=ActiveCampaign&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_content=Chef%20Sean%20Brock%20brings%20Appalachian%20food%20to%20the%20masses&amp;utm_campaign=Wednesday%2C%20August%2016%2C%202023" target=_blank>Cardinal News</a>.</i></div></div></div><div id=znid-830803473198 class=zn-element-wrapper data-type=horizontal_line data-full-width=false data-background-type=none data-shadow-enable=false><div class="zn-element zn-lg"><div class=zn-horizontal-line><hr></div></div></div><div id=znid-325892760740 class=zn-element-wrapper data-type=text data-background-type=none data-border-enable=false data-shadow-enable=false data-text-shadow-enable=false><div class="zn-element zn-lg"><div class=zn-text><a href=http://www.littmanwrites.com/ target=_blank>Margaret Littman</a> is a writer in Nashville who tells the stories of the people and places of the South.&nbsp;</div></div></div><div id=znid-528966895269 class=zn-element-wrapper data-type=row data-layout="8-4 8-4 12-12" data-vertical-align=center data-border-enable=true data-full-width=false data-background-type=none data-shadow-enable=false><div class="zn-element zn-lg"><div class=zn-row data-reverse-lg=false data-reverse-md=false data-reverse-sm=false><div class="zn-column zn-column-lg-8 zn-column-md-8 zn-column-sm-12"><div class=zn-children><div class=zn-child><div class=zn-template><div id=znid-404292636426 class=zn-element-wrapper data-type=banner data-full-width=false data-effect=none data-border-enable=false data-shadow-enable=false><div class="zn-element zn-lg"><div class=zn-banner tabindex=0 role=link><div class=zn-children-container><div class=zn-children><div class=zn-child><div class=zn-template><div id=znid-404598716931 class=zn-element-wrapper data-type=row data-background-type=none data-layout="12 12 12" data-full-width=false data-vertical-align=top